# Ecommerce-Agent v0.6.2

Multi-agent e-commerce content generation pipeline for 舒特工贸.

## What this project does

Transforms product descriptions into:
- 4-grid Gem Image / Imagen Prompts (463:278, 4K)
- AI-generated product images (Vertex AI Imagen)
- PPTX product catalogs
- Interactive HTML catalogs
- Social media copy (Facebook HPD + TikTok @hpdun3)
- Shopify store content (hpdun.com)

## Architecture

```
skills/ (23 skills)
  ├── production/ (5): product-analyzer, image-prompt-generator, image-generator, catalog-generator, html-generator
  ├── review/ (7): prompt-review, prompt-refactor, image-quality-review, listing-review, code-review, translation-qa, reflection
  ├── operations/ (8): competitor-analysis, ecommerce-analysis, seo-checklist, security-checklist, mobile-ux-checklist, content-calendar, architecture-review, debug-checklist
  ├── orchestration/ (2): context-compress, workflow-optimize
  └── social/ (1): social-copywriter

config/
  agents.yaml    — 8 agent definitions with skill bindings
  pipeline.yaml  — 10-stage pipeline (v2.0)
  tasks.yaml     — task definitions (v2.0)
  rules.yaml     — rule + skill index

playbooks/
  multi_agent_collaboration.md — 10-phase execution playbook (v2.0)

scripts/
  generate_images.py — Vertex AI Imagen batch generation
```

## Key files for AI

- `Agents.md` — AI development OS (entry point)
- `.cursor/rules/multi-agent.mdc` — Multi-agent pipeline entry
- `.cursor/rules/ecommerce.mdc` — E-commerce specific rules
- `.cursor/rules/coding.mdc` — Coding standards
- `ProductRule.md` — Product constraint rules
- `GemPrompt.md` — Prompt example
